{"type":"message","id":"713cd1ae","parentId":"c4847102","timestamp":"2026-03-29T02:37:49.000Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"好的，让我整理一下已安装的技能列表，包括所有来源的技能。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"你安装了以下技能（按来源分类）：\n\n## 🎨 用户自定义技能\n路径：`~/.agents/skills/`\n- **agent-browser** - 浏览器自动化\n- **find-skills** - 技能发现和安装\n\n## 🔌 Coze 插件技能\n路径：`/workspace/projects/extensions/coze-openclaw-plugin/skills/`\n- **coze-asr** - Coze 语音转文字\n- **coze-image-gen** - Coze 图片生成\n- **coze-tts** - Coze 文字转语音\n- **openclaw-faq** - OpenClaw/龙虾/扣子常见问题解答\n\n## 🐦 飞书插件技能\n路径：`/workspace/projects/extensions/openclaw-lark/skills/`\n- **feishu-bitable** - 飞书多维表格管理\n- **feishu-calendar** - 飞书日历与日程管理\n- **feishu-channel-rules** - 飞书频道输出规则\n- **feishu-create-doc** - 创建飞书云文档\n- **feishu-fetch-doc** - 获取飞书云文档内容\n- **feishu-im-read** - 飞书 IM 消息读取\n- **feishu-task** - 飞书任务管理\n- **feishu-troubleshoot** - 飞书插件问题排查\n- **feishu-update-doc** - 更新飞书云文档\n\n## 💼 企业微信插件技能\n路径：`/workspace/projects/extensions/wecom-openclaw-plugin/skills/`\n- **wecom-contact-lookup** - 通讯录成员查询\n- **wecom-doc-manager** - 企业微信文档管理\n- **wecom-edit-todo** - 企业微信待办事项编辑\n- **wecom-get-todo-detail** - 企业微信待办详情查询\n- **wecom-get-todo-list** - 企业微信待办列表查询\n- **wecom-meeting-create** - 企业微信会议创建\n- **wecom-meeting-manage** - 企业微信会议管理\n- **wecom-meeting-query** - 企业微信会议查询\n- **wecom-msg** - 企业微信消息\n- **wecom-preflight** - 企业微信插件前置条件检查\n- **wecom-schedule** - 企业微信日程管理\n- **wecom-send-media** - 企业微信多媒体发送\n- **wecom-smartsheet-data** - 企业微信智能表格数据管理\n- **wecom-smartsheet-schema** - 企业微信智能表格结构管理\n\n## ⚙️ OpenClaw 内置技能\n路径：`/usr/lib/node_modules/openclaw/skills/`\n- **1password** - 1Password 密码管理\n- **apple-notes** - Apple Notes 笔记\n- **apple-reminders** - Apple Reminders 提醒\n- **bear-notes** - Bear 笔记\n- **blogwatcher** - 博客监控\n- **blucli** - BluOS 音乐控制\n- **bluebubbles** - BlueBubbles iMessage\n- **camsnap** - 相机截图\n- **canvas** - Canvas 控制\n- **clawhub** - ClawHub 技能市场\n- **coding-agent** - 编程代理\n- **discord** - Discord 集成\n- **eightctl** - Eight Sleep 控制\n- **gemini** - Gemini AI\n- **gh-issues** - GitHub Issues\n- **gifgrep** - GIF 搜索\n- **github** - GitHub 集成\n- **gog** - GOG 游戏\n- **goplaces** - 地理位置服务\n- **healthcheck** - 安全加固和风险配置\n- **himalaya** - Himalaya 邮件客户端\n- **imsg** - iMessage\n- **mcporter** - Minecraft 端口转发\n- **model-usage** - 模型使用监控\n- **nano-banana-pro** - Nano Banana Pro\n- **nano-pdf** - PDF 处理\n- **node-connect** - 节点连接诊断\n- **notion** - Notion 笔记\n- **obsidian** - Obsidian 笔记\n- **openai-image-gen** - OpenAI 图片生成\n- **openai-whisper** - Whisper 语音识别（本地）\n- **openai-whisper-api** - Whisper API 语音识别\n- **openhue** - Philips Hue 灯光控制\n- **oracle** - Oracle 数据库\n- **ordercli** - 订单管理\n- **peekaboo** - Peekaboo 监控\n- **sag** - ElevenLabs TTS\n- **session-logs** - 会话日志\n- **sherpa-onnx-tts** - Sherpa-ONNX TTS\n- **skill-creator** - 技能创建工具\n- **slack** - Slack 集成\n- **songsee** - 歌曲识别\n- **sonoscli** - Sonos 音响控制\n- **spotify-player** - Spotify 播放器\n- **summarize** - 文本摘要\n- **things-mac** - Things 任务管理\n- **tmux** - Tmux 会话控制\n- **trello** - Trello 项目管理\n- **video-frames** - 视频帧提取\n- **voice-call** - 语音通话\n- **wacli** - WhatsApp CLI\n- **weather** - 天气查询\n- **xurl** - URL 工具\n\n---\n\n**总计：72 个技能**（27 个自定义 + 45 个内置）"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"coze","model":"auto","usage":{"input":2595,"output":1264,"cacheRead":41472,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":45331,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774751846486}}
